name: Xev Bellringer
description:
I think it speaks for itself, use with the tag 'xbv1' for slightly better results. Works well with dreamshaper, deliberate and analogMadness, but haven't had too much trouble in other ones I been playing with. It does lean towards the nsfw so you may want to put nsfw etc. in the negative prompt if that isn't what you're going for. Trained with 31 high-res images with no edits. Anyways... Enjoy!

Note:
Someone asked for the rest of the generation data in a comment on an image, so I replaced the images (which deleted the comment...oops :/ ) with the ones from the output folder, apparently moving them to another drive, messed with the png headers somehow? Idk whatever, it's fixed now :) apologies
